SupplierEvaluationContext is a Form
    Layout
        single column
            visible when (Description entered)
                PerformanceEvaluationTemplate.Name
                    label is "PerformanceEvaluationTemplate"
                    display as text
        single column
            Description
        paragraph
            visible when (IsEvaluationComplete)
                EvaluationCompletionDate
                    label is "CompletionDate"
                    display as text
